b361c9cd69265090220","tid":255641,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天文台用咁多錢搞預報系統結果先係事後先判斷，不如請幾個阿婆望天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a803a427b459fe6d17274615b0dc034f6a4c470f","tid":255641,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌你老母搵我去做天文台台長都得<br />\n場雨最大果陣唔識掛，永遠過左最大雨勢之後先識掛黑雨<br />\n你會發現黑雨掛左之後場雨反而細左<br />\n有邊次唔係咁？<br />\n屌你老母做天文台做到咁後知後覺搵阿婆去做都得</blockquote><br />\n一早講天文台唔係為香港人 係為經濟<br />\n天文台屬經濟發展局已經知咩料啦"},{"pid":"0e5b0cf875a7e48fb08dd78207f4325d4b619b56","tid":255641,"uid":25754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/132855_aa84d1a52d783deaba4214dc07c15805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F132855_aa84d1a52d783deaba4214dc07c15805.jpg&h=a38173b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16cf90c6154cd60f2eeed487171a2656eb3422dc","tid":255641,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文台根本係垃圾，完全唔保障到市民安全<br />\n<br />\n大雨到仆哂街都唔掛黃紅黑雨，咁對市民有乜警示作用，我夠睇到出面落大雨，但我唔知有幾嚴重喎<br />\n<br />\n屌你過哂氣先同我講黑雨？咁你有撚用咩食屎狗天文台</blockquote><br />\n邊個話保障市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路都係保商家"},{"pid":"05c1f912e785b0f5ff8ded9f79594bdabd3d2a2a","tid":255641,"uid":20622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n次次最大果陣黃雨<br />\n差唔多停雨先黑雨<br />\n屌你老母天文台"},{"pid":"b526724f788e43f801897398e1ca73a7a11458b6","tid":255641,"uid":102562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"根本6點幾就估到會超大雨"},{"pid":"37d6b596a6aedd7d45805d17c4c778f6f0267c31","tid":255641,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"天氣報告完畢。"},{"pid":"8f1ff678fb83c0ac814ca2a1c4c64aff8631a45a","tid":255641,"uid":14833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"炒股大過天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b506c03e49bf413ef41aaeac90b740600e70a29","tid":255641,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文台根本係垃圾，完全唔保障到市民安全<br />\n<br />\n大雨到仆哂街都唔掛黃紅黑雨，咁對市民有乜警示作用，我夠睇到出面落大雨，但我唔知有幾嚴重喎<br />\n<br />\n屌你過哂氣先同我講黑雨？咁你有撚用咩食屎狗天文台</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意，警報係最基本作用係等市民知道現時同埋即將既雨勢，等大家去判斷要點樣返工返學。<br />\n<br />\n停雨先掛黑雨，根據失去左預測既原意，不如天文台明天先掛返黑雨，話比大家尋日既雨勢去到黑雨水平"},{"pid":"955fb9983bb8d9a502daa30c44a4a45248de8145","tid":255641,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小明住大埔，7點45分出門口，黑雨程度，掛黃雨<br />\n小明公司係中環，黃雨程度，掛黃雨<br />\n8點50分，小明到左中環，黃雨程度，掛黃雨<br />\n9點15分，中環紅雨程度，掛紅雨，大埔雨勢開始減弱<br />\n11點30分，中環黑雨程度，掛黑雨，大埔停雨</blockquote><br />\n咁大個人仲要新界出港島番工真係陰公<br />\n學下人啦 踩單車番工<br />\n咪又唔會塞車同無位泊車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大個人仲要依賴交通工具返工，正廢物"},{"pid":"b72bfd57498a1ae5484bee86c554b13c6c7a651d","tid":255641,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>天文台用咁多錢搞預報系統結果先係事後先判斷，不如請幾個阿婆望天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到個畫面"},{"pid":"243ad22e750e1f754f7071e543e906e49fdb19a1","tid":255641,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"係個制度問題<br />\n唔知係落到幾高先掛黑雨"},{"pid":"2b779c5da2fdc9d2518e698b0fc2bf35b21211f9","tid":255641,"uid":33898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:39:03.000Z","msg":"等睇痴線黃雨搞出人命果陣班撚樣點兜"},{"pid":"edbfd8be71cb6d792e28d985c84c38048daadde3","tid":255641,"uid":110486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"都on9,掛一掛黑雨誠哥少幾個億你賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"3ac7aaf5b94fbd39391db56241485e481786c288","tid":255641,"uid":102826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"搵個弱智既做都得，總之返工時間過左先上紅雨就得"},{"pid":"5c68138da99b25d171a3b26f80f2cf8b69c54ec8","tid":255641,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:40:43.000Z","msg":"天文台死全家啦"},{"pid":"5d5ab7052b54b78e06a21b1d239dba84a6ed6cd4","tid":255641,"uid":110486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"其實收工黑雨人人OT仲爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220d549bfd194c2efa5a8b2804428cd0fe020985","tid":255641,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"天文台on撚9"},{"pid":"a52be438732ffb7d8624d37c1502b7a4a6bf79e1","tid":255641,"uid":35696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>天文台用咁多錢搞預報系統結果先係事後先判斷，不如請幾個阿婆望天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"