:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"天文台係咪要等到全港地區(中環)落到夠數先掛黑雨?"},{"pid":"5f390d24a0d801ea6f47ca62c389e1f80424482d","tid":255641,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"認真問，天文台死都唔掛黑雨有冇人吹得佢脹"},{"pid":"cc4586d98105320b221d66fddfacefd06e481360","tid":255641,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝舊石係到好過班廢柴科學主任啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/152102_3adc623684f73f76ceb20e794ede1998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F152102_3adc623684f73f76ceb20e794ede1998.jpg&h=c7c306ee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e754a247e831d9663ce1fa8c00270437e59d128","tid":255641,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"應該解散天文台<br />\n再一人一票投選天文台各職位"},{"pid":"b9f1e8e9c45b6eaa5ab6e56c2910c7c7ebe8e9f9","tid":255641,"uid":30845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:26:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 ''即時預報''"},{"pid":"3310f514165893e749e82f89f14a09c176bceb6a","tid":255641,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"港共政府班官只會為兩種人服務<br />\n一個係中共, 一個係商家<br />\n天文台好明顯就係為商家服務"},{"pid":"fba04f158b95c10baf59e0796e41d2b914feb5f5","tid":255641,"uid":6706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"今次我都唔撐天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712e81adf9ddd4841f849dadba6b4292036c47a0","tid":255641,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"申訴專員公署有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a21ffdee186f540ed40d69aa94727772d98cf73","tid":255641,"uid":26220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文台用咁多錢搞預報系統結果先係事後先判斷，<span style=\"color: red;\">不如請幾個阿婆望天</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你點解我會笑到想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ba715e1021311829bd5e2fd842514922872753","tid":255641,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"因為香港就算個降雨量/風幾勁都好<br />\n一定會減弱同埋唔會點做成人命傷亡<br />\n你想大交合學乖D 就要死多D人<br />\n比人屌撚到佢飛天下次先會早D掛"},{"pid":"a688f4a7cea44d18f520b3ddab8ae53b9e2f5413","tid":255641,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4a0799702d366f77f2992ddfba7c529ba886bea","tid":255641,"uid":67067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"真係on撚鳩 <br />\n我番工個頭低地 <br />\n黑雨個日番去開去 <br />\n水浸到on9 <br />\n我屌你老母"},{"pid":"42bcaacfb38a41c5096824c8b16bb0cd9442f34a","tid":255641,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當你果到天晴但掛黑雨你又屌<br />\n<br />\n唔夠大雨掛黑雨你又屌<br />\n<br />\n剩係你果到大雨就掛黑雨咩<br />\n講緊全香港架嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大交合職員？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問幾時發生過上述情況？而且我相信唔屌多過屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今朝好明顯全港都好大雨，有曬實測<br />\n絕對可以早d出黑雨<br />\n完全係天文台責任無得怪市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成個香港個個地區D人都屌緊點解咁大雨都唔掛黑雨<br />\n你仲夠膽講&quot;剩係你果到大雨就掛黑雨咩&quot;<br />\n到底你係真港豬定大交合職員?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我既同事分別住係<br />\n大嶼山/北區/黃大仙區/南區 同埋我西貢區<br />\n<br />\n全部都話出門番工好撚大雨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3a2263a29520364afddb9e2ab9dd6f121b7508","tid":255641,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該解散天文台<br />\n再一人一票投選天文台各職位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n選佢老母臭閪咩<br />\n請四個人三班制嘅報導員就ok. <br />\n使撚用成個廢柴垃圾天文臺部門<br />\n一年D錢用嚟濟貧好過"},{"pid":"558c48b10e928909093cb55059707a416bb4a68d","tid":255641,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實天文台只要請個parttime<br />\n響京士柏露天坐響度， 到場雨落到最勁果陣<br />\n先施施然打番中環個office,正式掛黑雨<br />\n完全唔需要電腦，果d 咩超級電腦完全嘥電<br />\n<br />\n再者天文台使撚office,比個茶水阿組咁大既位佢就夠</blockquote><br />\n天文台office係尖沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6722af9dfdbfbda692347ac1c4f2ca290f8807c6","tid":255641,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"開左市先<br />\n跟住先掛番d紅呀黑呀 叫做有掛過<br />\n市民屌呀?<br />\n關佢撚事?"},{"pid":"1101aa6588fab1a0f31a8b800c43518d21c24f1d","tid":255641,"uid":14013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:10:10.000Z","msg":"打風，黃紅黑雨我都睇撚化哂<br />\n問題係，依幾年睇天氣預測，我係講緊預測聽日既天氣<br />\n唔係幾日後，都夠膽死相差十幾度<br />\n好！我試下幫天交合兜，實係全球暖化<br />\n搞到天氣溫度唔穩定<br />\n但我屌你老母！你同我講聽日落雨<br />\n去到第二日，曬撚到我鳩到縮<br />\n睇返天交合個app，即刻show老撚咁大個太陽出黎<br />\n我屌你老母呀！仲話換乜撚野超級電腦<br />\n係咪換撚埋做windows98呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a7d5946ae2b8ecc1ac24996374cfd8e72b2119","tid":255641,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"無論呢個政府做乜, 都實有人衝出黎話佢做得好, 做得冇錯, <br />\n<br />\n所以你地點屌都冇用架, 因為佢會話有其他市民支持, <br />\n<br />\n係呢個PO 就見到有人護航啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ab97be85aeb59be36e84b748bf0c0acd74242d","tid":255641,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"永遠唔可以0930前掛黑雨<br />\n呢個係一個不敗之謎。"},{"pid":"d62184d508f2ea8ab25c403ffa70ebf6446cc300","tid":255641,"uid":63618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:03:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母用咁撚多錢搞咩超級電腦都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n18區每區請幾個part time，每次有雨就放個指定既杯出戶外，每15分鐘就whatsapp報一次雨量，平均數一過某個數就出警報，又快又準又代表全港雨量啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打風都係一樣原理<br />\n<br />\n天氣預報跟本我出街前望個天仲準過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔撚係都多雲局部地區有驟雨，但就永遠唔係我會經過既地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人手測都一定準過依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4243120fd98b80abe15679d6d966f9186b94310d","tid":255641,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"天文台愈來愈垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a20e67896fffec36bdccbaeebcc209e97813fd","tid":255641,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"屌7佢，條撚樣真係唔撚識掛"},{"pid":"c2836345bf47c3350e193d6f928c270fbfcb56ed","tid":255641,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"agree<br />\n我屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4bd1e72a6ee827d5e095abf5fcbe754785d326","tid":255641,"uid":37770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"今日都證明左天文台係做show<br />\n出門口勁撚大雨-黃雨<br />\n9:15 返哂工-紅黑<br />\n11:30 黑色，個個以為下午收工<br />\n12:30 黃雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  冇半日收，繼續返工"},{"pid":"51fcf9e2d2d1f85b49c87b93bcde8059b3e7c777","tid":255641,"uid":17692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:29:44.000Z","msg":"日本仔個天文台可以 預報 一陣會好大雨係有實數咁報定先。11點已經講定12點會大雨成點<br />\n<br />\n香港個垃圾天文台 只係機械人咁到數就出警告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【発表時刻】<br />\n5月8日12:20<br />\n<br />\n強い雨（21mm/h）の予測をお知らせします。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【予測される雨量】<br />\n12:20～ 10mm/h<br />\n12:30～ 12mm/h<br />\n12:40～ 19mm/h<br />\n12:50～ 21mm/h<br />\n13:00～ 16mm/h<br />\n13:10～ 9mm/h"},{"pid":"8969a08bf8b77f2baf06fe9f7e1f1f45fe40c905","tid":255641,"uid":10922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"最撚無用既部門，執撚左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a742049f22df24cf9500ef694c22e1c7bf20ff","tid":255641,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本仔個天文台可以 預報 一陣會好大雨係有實數咁報定先。11點已經講定12點會大雨成點<br />\n<br />\n香港個垃圾天文台 只係機械人咁到數就出警告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【発表時刻】<br />\n5月8日12:20<br />\n<br />\n強い雨（21mm/h）の予測をお知らせします。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【予測される雨量】<br />\n12:20～ 10mm/h<br />\n12:30～ 12mm/h<br />\n12:40～ 19mm/h<br />\n12:50～ 21mm/h<br />\n13:00～ 16mm/h<br />\n13:10～ 9mm/h</blockquote><br />\n日本仲可以分區睇"},{"pid":"fbb4ce19fdd500014b5c68cd2e58d0db10256dd8","tid":255641,"uid":37474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打風，黃紅黑雨我都睇撚化哂<br />\n問題係，依幾年睇天氣預測，我係講緊預測聽日既天氣<br />\n唔係幾日後，都夠膽死相差十幾度<br />\n好！我試下幫天交合兜，實係全球暖化<br />\n搞到天氣溫度唔穩定<br />\n但我屌你老母！你同我講聽日落雨<br />\n去到第二日，曬撚到我鳩到縮<br />\n睇返天交合個app，即刻show老撚咁大個太陽出黎<br />\n我屌你老母呀！仲話換乜撚野超級電腦<br />\n係咪換撚埋做windows98呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n駁唔撚度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13857a7a4bdb8df4b84724f3875ffe3b8328d5e6","tid":255641,"uid":66597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:47:56.000Z","msg":"得閒mon下天文台都知佢柒下柒下 根本唔係預報係匯報 撞正打風落雨就柒都兩錢重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有成個夏天等撚住大交合柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43761aac155c5992de94cb2dfd47168a2281484","tid":255641,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"8號風球好似都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317e126f19232a45e2641468743f6f06a77f3d1d","tid":255641,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:07:01.000Z","msg":"對慣香港個垃圾天文台 去一轉日本就會覺得日本天氣預測好似神算咁 話幾時落就幾時落幾時停就幾時停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e23cd24f0906a19564f42a843ea2515985a942","tid":255641,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母用咁撚多錢搞咩超級電腦都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n18區每區請幾個part time，每次有雨就放個指定既杯出戶外，每15分鐘就whatsapp報一次雨量，平均數一過某個數就出警報，又快又準又代表全港雨量啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打風都係一樣原理<br />\n<br />\n天氣預報跟本我出街前望個天仲準過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔撚係都多雲局部地區有驟雨，但就永遠唔係我會經過既地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人手測都一定準過依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實連登已經做到<br />\n下次大雨開post，每區搵人報吿雨量<br />\n有冇人有興趣，而家可以諗諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674c2d8bf91e95e17806198765953417c681857c","tid":255641,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對慣香港個垃圾天文台 去一轉日本就會覺得日本天氣預測好似神算咁 話幾時落就幾時落幾時停就幾時停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係佢唔做姐，有衛星睇住，幾日後就話難估姐，依家講今日或者聽日，睇撚住舊雲埋緊黎，又明知係雨雲，唔通仲可以天晴咩"},{"pid":"11b0cd425bf9241fb746e4d2d803cbdbd253bc9e","tid":255641,"uid":51604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"先唔講黑雨 掛左紅雨先 少咁班學生起碼冇咁塞車先<br />\n黑雨唔係一起身就掛左 冇乜切身影響<br />\n多數都返左工/到一半 落左仲要死返去<br />\n學生返少一日半日其實冇乜影響"},{"pid":"fe3a159f33d5af00b50f92927d3f6ae3a06fb3ee","tid":255641,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:29:43.000Z","msg":"而家最多俾你班賤民屌下，真係提早掛到時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e92d22e27f1b2d1e191aab6f183b03165614e4","tid":255641,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87a129c6b472ad73a4f5cefd6e512128df5fd46b","tid":255641,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40698cbd7815d828e410ed48a92c0f7605061750","tid":255641,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天文台屌極都係咁 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天文台都係打工啫<br />\n佢<span style=\"color: red;\">大老細</span>都咁on9<br />\n唔通佢可以醒目得去邊</blockquote><br />\n誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}